  "detailed_description": "Adrift in the Backrooms is online co-op adventure game up to 4 players where you and your friends explore, solve puzzles and try to find your way out. It takes some elements from the backrooms, but as a whole it's designed to offer a new experience for players. It's a refreshing mix of backrooms and more traditional horror/adventure games.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2>Explore 11 unique levels that each offer something different<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/ae38ba35c28dacbca184a04f31d4bf57.webp?t=1756678491\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/ae38ba35c28dacbca184a04f31d4bf57.poster.avif?t=1756678491\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=658 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Entities</h2>Encounter many entities with different behaviors<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/e7f2861b719adf3948debc8d8a9a125d.poster.avif?t=1756678491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/e7f2861b719adf3948debc8d8a9a125d.webm?t=1756678491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles</h2>Complete puzzles throughout the game<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/09b0ba65c8de13f66dc0d99b2d01b2f7.poster.avif?t=1756678491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/09b0ba65c8de13f66dc0d99b2d01b2f7.webm?t=1756678491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/09b0ba65c8de13f66dc0d99b2d01b2f7.mp4?t=1756678491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1-4 Player co-op</h2>Take your friends with you on a journey to the backrooms<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/2af2c53ab93e25b165194fada43ca852.poster.avif?t=1756678491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/2af2c53ab93e25b165194fada43ca852.webm?t=1756678491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Adrift in the Backrooms is online co-op adventure game up to 4 players where you and your friends explore, solve puzzles and try to find your way out. It takes some elements from the backrooms, but as a whole it's designed to offer a new experience for players. It's a refreshing mix of backrooms and more traditional horror/adventure games.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2>Explore 11 unique levels that each offer something different<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/ae38ba35c28dacbca184a04f31d4bf57.webp?t=1756678491\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/ae38ba35c28dacbca184a04f31d4bf57.poster.avif?t=1756678491\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=658 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Entities</h2>Encounter many entities with different behaviors<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/e7f2861b719adf3948debc8d8a9a125d.poster.avif?t=1756678491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/e7f2861b719adf3948debc8d8a9a125d.webm?t=1756678491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles</h2>Complete puzzles throughout the game<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/09b0ba65c8de13f66dc0d99b2d01b2f7.poster.avif?t=1756678491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524870/extras/09b0ba65c8de13f66dc0d99b2d01b2f7.webm?t=1756678491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/